a.n: The plague at the karatas village

p.k: Drama Kazakhstan (2016). Hrají: Aibek Kudabayev, Nurbek Mukushev, Tolganay Talgat. Režie: Adikhan Yerzhanov.
p.d: A new mayor comes to the remote village Karatas. A very strange illness reins over here. However somebody is used to live with it and says this is a simple flu.
